---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services" description="Bathroom remodels, kitchen renovations, tile work, and select full-home remodeling in Colorado. Quality craftsmanship, honest communication.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>What We Build</h1>
      <p>Focused expertise. Quality materials. Work we stand behind.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bathroom Remodels -->
  <section id="bathroom" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail">
        <h2>Bathroom Remodels</h2>
        <p class="lead">This is our primary focus—and where our craftsmanship shows most clearly.</p>

        <p>
          Bathrooms demand precision. Waterproofing has to be right. Tile work has to be level,
          aligned, and built to last. Fixtures need proper installation. We've refined our process
          over hundreds of projects, and it shows in the finished work.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're updating a dated guest bath, converting a tub to a walk-in shower, or
          gutting a master bathroom down to the studs, we bring the same attention to detail.
        </p>

        <div class="service-lists">
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>What's included</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Design consultation and layout planning</li>
              <li>Demolition and disposal</li>
              <li>Plumbing rough-in coordination</li>
              <li>Waterproofing and substrate preparation</li>
              <li>Tile installation (floors, walls, showers)</li>
              <li>Vanity and cabinetry installation</li>
              <li>Fixture and hardware installation</li>
              <li>Finish carpentry and trim</li>
              <li>Final cleanup and walkthrough</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Best for</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Full bathroom renovations</li>
              <li>Shower or tub-to-shower conversions</li>
              <li>Tile upgrades requiring proper waterproofing</li>
              <li>Aging-in-place modifications done right</li>
              <li>Anyone who's been burned by sloppy tile work before</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Not a fit if</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>You need a quick cosmetic refresh (paint, hardware swap)</li>
              <li>You're looking for the lowest possible bid</li>
              <li>The timeline is "as fast as possible" regardless of quality</li>
              <li>You want to supply your own materials without consultation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Kitchen Remodels -->
  <section id="kitchen" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail">
        <h2>Kitchen Remodels</h2>
        <p class="lead">A kitchen remodel is one of the largest investments you'll make in your home. We treat it that way.</p>

        <p>
          We help homeowners plan layouts that improve function, select materials that balance
          durability and aesthetics, and execute with the precision that complex kitchen work demands.
          From cabinet installation to tile backsplashes to coordinating countertop fabrication, we
          manage the details so you don't have to.
        </p>

        <div class="service-lists">
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>What's included</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Design consultation and layout planning</li>
              <li>Demolition and disposal</li>
              <li>Coordination with countertop fabricators</li>
              <li>Cabinet installation</li>
              <li>Tile backsplash installation</li>
              <li>Flooring installation</li>
              <li>Fixture and hardware installation</li>
              <li>Finish carpentry and trim</li>
              <li>Final cleanup and walkthrough</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Best for</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Full kitchen renovations</li>
              <li>Cabinet replacement projects</li>
              <li>Layout changes that improve workflow</li>
              <li>Homeowners who want quality materials installed correctly</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Not a fit if</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>You only need appliance replacement</li>
              <li>You're looking for cabinet refacing only</li>
              <li>Budget is the only deciding factor</li>
              <li>You need the work done in under two weeks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tile & Finish Work -->
  <section id="tile" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail">
        <h2>Tile & Finish Work</h2>
        <p class="lead">Tile work is where craftsmanship is most visible—and where shortcuts are impossible to hide.</p>

        <p>
          We specialize in precision tile installation for showers, floors, backsplashes, and
          feature walls. Our finish carpentry includes trim, built-ins, and the final details
          that complete a space. This is detail work, and we don't rush it.
        </p>

        <div class="service-lists">
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>What's included</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Surface preparation and substrate work</li>
              <li>Waterproofing (wet areas)</li>
              <li>Tile layout and installation</li>
              <li>Grout and sealing</li>
              <li>Trim and finish carpentry</li>
              <li>Cleanup and final inspection</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Best for</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Custom shower tile installations</li>
              <li>Floor tile (ceramic, porcelain, natural stone)</li>
              <li>Backsplash installations</li>
              <li>Accent walls and feature tilework</li>
              <li>Trim and millwork upgrades</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Not a fit if</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>You need a single small repair (broken tile, cracked grout line)</li>
              <li>You want peel-and-stick or snap-together flooring</li>
              <li>The job is under 50 square feet</li>
              <li>Speed matters more than precision</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Full-Home Remodels -->
  <section id="full-home" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-detail">
        <h2>Select Full-Home Remodels</h2>
        <p class="lead">For the right projects, we take on comprehensive renovations.</p>

        <p>
          Full-home remodels require careful coordination across multiple trades, consistent
          quality control, and clear communication throughout a longer timeline. We're selective
          about these projects because we won't compromise our standards to take on more work.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you're considering a significant renovation, let's talk. We'll be honest about
          whether it's a fit.
        </p>

        <div class="service-lists">
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>What's included</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Comprehensive project planning</li>
              <li>Coordination of all trades (electrical, plumbing, HVAC as needed)</li>
              <li>Permit management</li>
              <li>Quality control across all phases</li>
              <li>Regular progress updates</li>
              <li>Final walkthrough and punch list</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Best for</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Major renovations with realistic timelines</li>
              <li>Projects where consistent quality across the home matters</li>
              <li>Homeowners who want one point of contact managing everything</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-list">
            <h4>Not a fit if</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>You need the project completed in an aggressive timeframe</li>
              <li>Budget is tight and flexibility is limited</li>
              <li>You prefer to self-manage multiple contractors</li>
              <li>The scope keeps changing without willingness to adjust timeline or budget</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to discuss your project?</h2>
      <p>Free consultations. Honest conversations about scope, timeline, and fit.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .service-detail {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .service-detail .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .service-lists {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .service-lists {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .service-list h4 {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .service-list ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
</style>
